---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { info } from "../data/info";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <header class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="space-y-4 order-2 sm:order-1">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent">
          About
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text dark:text-dk-text leading-relaxed">
          <strong>{info.name}</strong> is a
          <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_engineering">
            full-stack engineer</a>
          with a background in
          <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_intelligence">
            business intelligence</a>
          and
          <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economics">
            economics</a>.
          He helps businesses turn complex data and processes into solutions that drive results.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 sm:order-2 shrink-0">
        <Image
          src={info.picture}
          alt={info.picture_alt}
          width={96}
          height={96}
          class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full object-cover grayscale contrast-115 shadow-sm border border-text/10 dark:border-dk-text/10"
        />
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="space-y-6 mt-6 mb-6 text-text/90 dark:text-dk-text/90 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
        About Nick
      </h2>
      <p>
        His professional journey began in academia, producing a
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/posts/making-nuclear-energy-competitve-with-fossil-fuels-and-natural-gas">report</a>
        for the
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://ners.engin.umich.edu/">University of Michigan's NERS department</a>
        on the economics of nuclear reactors in the United States.
      </p>
      <p>
        From there he moved into BI, building dashboards, automating reports, and digging into data
        to make it useful for people. Nick worked for one of Michigan's premier economic development
        firms, <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://rightplace.org">The Right Place, Inc</a>,
        providing the public with economic
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://www.rightplace.org/news/west-michigan-businesses-plan-to-increase-wages-between-3-2-to-4-6-in-2023">reports</a>
        and helping kickstart key
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://rightplace.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/production/uploads/downloads/public-resources/State-of-the-Region-2022_FINAL.pdf">regional data reports</a>.
        His data, charts, and analysis were featured in the
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://www.wzzm13.com/article/money/economy/the-right-place-sees-positive-future-for-west-michigan-at-economic-outlook-presentation/69-cdbf79c8-3edc-4ae9-a642-8c4dea266d69">news</a>
        alongside Michigan's top economic leaders.
      </p>
      <p>
        His work evolved into building enterprise software that helps businesses run smoother and
        make better decisions, leading to the creation of
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://luniv.tech">Luniv Technology</a>,
        a small software shop Nick founded.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nick holds a bachelor's degree in economics and philosophy, combining analytical thinking
        with business acumen and technical expertise. His work primarily focuses on
        <strong>Elixir, .NET, Go, and JavaScript.</strong>
      </p>

      <section class="pt-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
          Personal Interests
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text/80 dark:text-dk-text/80">
          <li>Writing on <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/posts">his blog</a> 📝</li>
          <li>Reading books 📚</li>
          <li>Cooking! 🍳</li>
          <li>Producing music through Ableton and hardware like MIDIs and drum machines</li>
          <li>Exercising, hiking, and running races 🏃‍♂️</li>
          <li>Traveling, especially around the United States - see his trips to
            <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/posts/chicago">Chicago</a> and
            <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/posts/houston">Houston</a> ✈️
          </li>
          <li>Hanging out with his dog,
            <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/bruce-the-dog">Bruce</a> 🐕
          </li>
          <li>Exploring trends in technology, business, and economics 📈</li>
          <li>Video games, mainly FPS like
            <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://dayz.com/">DayZ</a> and
            <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://www.counter-strike.net/">Counter Strike</a> 🎮
          </li>
          <li>Football, the good kind ⚽</li>
          <li>Experimenting with new programming languages 🛠️</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
    <section class="pt-6">
         <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
        Subscribing
      </h2>
      <p>You can subscribe to this website using <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/rss.xml">RSS.</a></p>
    </section>
    <section class="pt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
        About this site
      </h2>
      <p>
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/">nickstambaugh.dev</a> is built with <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a>.
        The code is hosted on
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://github.com/sieep-coding/sieep-coding.github.io">GitHub</a>
        and deployed via <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel</a>.
        This site contains no advertisements. If you want to show some love,
        <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/nickstambaugh">buy Nick a coffee</a> ☕
      </p>

      <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-text/10 dark:border-dk-text/10">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="text-sm text-text/60 dark:text-dk-text/60 hover:text-secondary dark:hover:text-dk-accent transition-colors"
        >
          ← Back to home
        </a>
      </footer>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
